Directed by: @nesmithjosh 

OUT NOW via @higherfrequencyrecordings 🌊☁️🏔

“The inspiration for this song was conceived by honoring the union of the Divine Masculine & Feminine Energies coming together as one, opening the portal of creation & guiding the vessel through its daily rituals. This sacred bond within ourselves & with others gives birth to new life & the experiences that we seek to manifest.” - Sky 🎨⛲️🎵

Team Member Highlight: 

Jondel is a body builder who knows the importance of investing in yourself. He’s providing his clients great value and helping them achieve their dreams EveryDay!

He says, “My experience with EDST has been the embodiment of helping people not only achieve their dreams but being a part of a family.” 

#EDST

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by EDST 📲 on July 27, 2021 tagging @jamell_nyt. May be an image of 3 people, people standing, wrist watch and indoor.

node.text:
“How does an independent artist like myself go from being homeless playing the subways of New York City, to rubbing elbows and collaboratong with the top artists, producers, and Dj’s in the industry?

IT’S SIMPLE!! EDST
BUILD YOUR BRAND!!!!

If you are only focusing on making music and shooting music videos you are doing it wrong 🤷🏿‍♂️
The entertainment business is ALL about  perception!  There’s  talented people everywhere 🤷🏿‍♂️ but Your image, your credibility, and the relationships you create within your Network determine your success. It doesn’t matter how hot your music is, how many songs you have on your laptop, or how many celebrities you claim to know. Nobody is getting on the boat until they see other ppl on the boat 🙅🏿‍♂️ if you aren’t investing in MARKETING, MANAGEMENT, & PROMOTION, and you have no image and no credibility how do you expect to get anywhere?” 
- @jamell_nyt

node.text:
Team Member Highlight: 

Pac’Liyah recently joined the team & she’s absolutely killing it! She’s an Atlanta based Rapper, Singersongwriter, Event Curator, Record Label Owner & Digital Marketing Executive! 🔥

She says, “I just feel like if you want a change in your life, you can’t wait for it. Change comes through challenge & creation..If you’re not willing to challenge yourself and create the life you want for yourself, it’ll be hard to experience true progression. Boss up & make your next move, your BEST move. EDST was a chess move for me💯” 

#EDST

node.text:
Team Member Highlight: 

Sean knows the importance of investing in your brand. It doesn’t matter how great your content is if no one is seeing it! 

He says, “Working with EDST has transformed my way of thinking when it comes to promotional strategy. I came onboard with a ton of great content that no one ever got a chance to enjoy. Now I'm getting my music, my brand and my clothing in front of thousands of new eyes daily. I also aquired a new business mindset that I am applying to my marketing moves as a Manager. EDST is an instant game changer for the inspired entrepreneurs ready to change their lives. I am proud to now be among that category.” 

#EDST

I’m beyond grateful to be apart of it.” #EDST

node.text:
Team Member Highlight: 

Jake is nothing but good vibes & we are so grateful to have him on the team! He’s providing the necessary support & value for his clients to thrive online. 

He says, “it wasn’t until my cousin @jarredrosenberg opened up this new door in my life that has brought nothing but amazing people and amazing opportunities. If I could offer it to everyone I would. Everyday success team has been a blessing in disguise and if I could give any advice, hop on the wagon before it’s too late! Everyday you wait is just one more day your competition gets ahead of you! I love the team I have joined, but more importantly love the family I have gained in the process!”

#EDST
